playstore_details.title: Free Music & Videos - Music Player for YouTube
playstore_details.description:
Free Music & Videos is a free music player and stream music service for YouTube. Discover free music through top charts - find free music videos, hot music, new music, get free songs recommendations from YouTube and stream music unlimited. Save your favorite songs to playlists or import playlists from your account so that your free music is always with you.
Free Music & Videos free music player is best of all free music apps. Forget about background music player - now you can stream free music while you browse news or chat with friends thanks to the floating pop-up YouTube music player. Having a small dimensions pop-up YouTube music player will not overlap your screen and will allow you to enjoy listening to free music while doing other tasks. No need for music download: stream free music for free and save space on your phone.

YOUTUBE FREE MUSIC
• Best music library you can find is well organized in Free Music & Videos - millions of free songs in your phone
• Explore top charts, featured playlists, find hot music and new music, get free music recommendations from YouTube
• Save your favorite free songs to playlists or import playlists from your account
• Discover free music and new music charts of your country

YOUTUBE MUSIC PLAYER
• No need for background music player. With pop-up YouTube music player you can stream music while doing other tasks
• One click to expand floating YouTube music player into powerful full screen music player
• No need for music download. Stream music and save space on your phone
• Move pop-up YouTube music player to any place on the screen

PLEASE NOTE
• Free Music & Videos does not let you to download music, download video or stream music in background due to YouTube Terms of Service
• All content is provided by YouTube services. This app does not have control over the content displayed
